### Bruce: Project Overview

- **Purpose**: Ergonomic, lightweight, pure Java wrapper around the Java Cryptography API (JCA)
- **Java version**: 17, Java modules enabled (`module-info.java`)
- **Main entry point**: `Bruce.java` facade offering static factory methods for crypto operations

