- [Bruce.java](mdc:src/main/java/com/mirkocaserta/bruce/Bruce.java)

#### Package Structure (public API)
- `com.mirkocaserta.bruce` — facade and builders
- `com.mirkocaserta.bruce.cipher.(symmetric|asymmetric)` — encryption/decryption
- `com.mirkocaserta.bruce.signature` — digital signatures and verification
- `com.mirkocaserta.bruce.digest` — message digests and file hashing
- `com.mirkocaserta.bruce.mac` — message authentication codes

#### Core Patterns
- **Facade**: `Bruce` exposes simplified APIs
- **Builder APIs**: `cipherBuilder()`, `signerBuilder()`, `verifierBuilder()`, `digestBuilder()`, `macBuilder()`
- **ByKey variants**: runtime key selection using maps
- **Encoding support**: `Encoding` enum (HEX, BASE64, URL, MIME)
- **Provider support**: optional `provider` parameter (e.g., "BC" for Bouncy Castle)